{"tid":659093,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"復仇者聯盟配對紋身示無忘六四","createTime":"2018-05-09T13:56:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T08:28:50.000Z","uid":165075,"like":727,"dislike":83,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"cb169245b6be52fd6527ee1dffa09a42e8bcc6d3","tid":659093,"uid":165075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T13:56:55.000Z","msg":"還有一個月便到中國的敏感日子, 復仇者聯盟一眾似乎也乘電影大捷，提醒全世界，地球尚有一個每年只有364日的地方。<br />\n<br />\n日前，黑寡婦帶領鷹眼、鐵甲奇俠、雷神及美國隊長到紋身師Josh Lord紋下這個紀念紋身。看似紀念Avengers 的圖案，細心看的話，不難看出另有玄機。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i65.tinypic.com/2uojlp2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi65.tinypic.com%2F2uojlp2.jpg&h=fc5ed7b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上圖為美國隊長為聯盟和紋身師影的合照，自己反而未能出鏡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i68.tinypic.com/6ynul4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi68.tinypic.com%2F6ynul4.jpg&h=ba8a6466&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i67.tinypic.com/16azhqs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi67.tinypic.com%2F16azhqs.jpg&h=3f7394a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然外國網站，如<a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/2018/5/8/17330668/avengers-infinity-war-tattoo-meaning-robert-downey-jr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.polygon.com%2F2018%2F5%2F8%2F17330668%2Favengers-infinity-war-tattoo-meaning-robert-downey-jr&d=a13b%2B%2F%2Bj0piFqaq4QyyA9Gi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=8679702b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.polygon.com/2018/5/8/17330668/avengers-infinity-war-tattoo-meaning-robert-downey-jr</a> 也有推測紋身的意思，但不明白國情的人，實在難以品味它的內涵。當然，紋身設計的事情很主觀，圖案的真正意思暫時也無人可以判斷。至於你信不信，我反正信了。<br />\n<br />\n圖片轉自Instagram 和 Entertainment Weekly<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/Bie3WhknTSQ/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBie3WhknTSQ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&d=a13b%2B%2F%2Bj0piFqaq4QyyA9Gi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=6b196f4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBie3WhknTSQ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&h=ba2483b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/Bie3WhknTSQ/?utm_source=ig_embed</a>"},{"pid":"83550f0321973519e2c7d671c1af197d2e4654bf","tid":659093,"uid":136770,"like":75,"dislike":16,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T13:58:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細思極恐"},{"pid":"0b2b6c9790dfe7816a6232802703ee41903a7a6b","tid":659093,"uid":41508,"like":1238,"dislike":6,"score":1232,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T13:59:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"44c4f435505ab59ad0d2372ef6a6b3a53286e0bc","tid":659093,"uid":11895,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T14:00:25.000Z","msg":"贏國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b5b2fa37fd21a1a3f49f74553e1e38b8cdc4fb","tid":659093,"uid":82532,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T14:00:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96359a9552f6c2c57f1417279f46805bfc49b82a","tid":659093,"uid":136770,"like":37,"dislike":4,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T14:01:53.000Z","msg":"去蚛蝈宣傳嗰陣咪要好似d球員咁<br />\n用繃帶包住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b18b97be419e2973c763a7eb5c155d0b917c7a3","tid":659093,"uid":46769,"like":62,"dislike":3,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T14:02:59.000Z","msg":"illuminati confirmed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c1257dbdee936390a4213bde7582215ac42df5","tid":659093,"uid":165075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"96359a9552f6c2c57f1417279f46805bfc49b82a","tid":65909